he face of competition from WeWork and Knotel, our CTO, Ben Nevile [ https:=
//link.sbstck.com/redirect/1afed0b5-3698-430c-9143-a8be3e7ae9f1?j=3DeyJ1Ijo=
iOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ], told us to read =
