-4135-98a1-4a30a8d16b69?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbq=
Osa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] by Richard Rumelt. Great rec.=C2=A0
It=E2=80=99s my favorite strategy book because it was so easy to put into p=
