a8b776798?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNp=
U ] for the conversation!=20
That=E2=80=99s all for today! We=E2=80=99ll be back in your inbox on Friday=
 with the Weekly Dose.=20
Thanks for reading,=20
