margin: 1em 0 0.625em 0; position: relative;"><strong>Bad Strategy</strong>=
</h3><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px=
; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Most capital-S Strategy, as it&#8217;s taught =
and practiced by people who call it Strategy, is </span><strong>Bad Strateg=
y</strong><span>.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-=
size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>When </span><a hr=
ef=3D"https://link.sbstck.com/redirect/0c03fcbe-6860-409b-b5a0-4be69d716f2a=
?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel st=
yle=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">Ben Rollert</a>=
<span> and I told Breather&#8217;s exec team that we were going to spend Ch=
ristmas break 2017 coming up with a strategy to improve our margins in the =
face of competition from WeWork and Knotel, our CTO, </span><a href=3D"http=
s://link.sbstck.com/redirect/1afed0b5-3698-430c-9143-a8be3e7ae9f1?j=3DeyJ1I=
joiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"col=
or: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">Ben Nevile</a><span>, tol=
d us to read </span><em><a href=3D"https://link.sbstck.com/redirect/46f2f7e=
2-b9e8-4135-98a1-4a30a8d16b69?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlX=
XepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration=
: underline;">Good Strategy Bad Strategy</a></em><span> by Richard Rumelt. =
Great rec.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 1=
6px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">It&#8217;s my favorite strateg=
y book because it was so easy to put into practice, and because I recognize=
d so many of the characteristics of bad strategy. Here are a few:</p><ul st=
yle=3D"margin-top: 0; padding: 0;"><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-s=
pecial-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, =
64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; p=
adding-left: 4px;"><strong>Mistaking Goals for Strategy</strong><span>: A c=
