li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><p style=
=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-h=
eight: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;"><strong>Fluff=
</strong><span>: Using buzzwords and jargon to create the illusion of high-=
level thinking. If you think strategy is bullshit, fluff is quite likely th=
e culprit.&#160;</span></p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-spec=
ial-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 64,=
 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padd=
ing-left: 4px;"><strong>Failure to Face the Challenge</strong><span>: There=
&#8217;s often one key thing that really matters for a business - Rumelt ca=
