le=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">here</a><span>.<=
/span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height:=
 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Not every idea has a viable path to defensibili=
ty. That&#8217;s OK. It&#8217;s better to toss the idea or decide to bootst=
rap after a couple weeks of researching and writing than it is to spend yea=
rs of your life and millions of dollars of other peoples&#8217; money going=
 the venture-backed route on something that you know ahead of time will pro=
bably fail. </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-h=
eight: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Knowing what game you should be playing i=
s strategy, too.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16=
px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><strong>Finally, if the founder=
s see a path to defensibility, they need to determine the one or two most i=
mportant challenges to address head-on.</strong><span>&#160;</span></p><p s=
tyle=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin:=
 0 0 20px 0;">Based on your diagnosis, what is the most critical solvable p=
roblem facing your company? Identify that upfront, and craft your strategy =
around solving it.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: =
16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>These will be different=
 for every business and every industry. In </span><em><a href=3D"https://li=
nk.sbstck.com/redirect/17f9ea38-dc15-4761-a507-66042a19d4d3?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXA=
wZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rg=
b(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">The Crux</a><span>, </span></em=
><span>Rumelt talks about Elon Musk realizing that launches were too expens=
ive to ever get humans to Mars, identifying reusability as the most importa=
nt issue to solve for affordability, and throwing all of his early resource=
s at reusability.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-=
size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Sometimes, the ch=
allenge will be so big that it&#8217;s worth throwing everything at solving=
 it before worrying about anything else. SpaceX didn&#8217;t develop Starli=
nk, which gives it </span><a href=3D"https://link.sbstck.com/redirect/796c2=
68b-a9f1-4f85-ae43-6c5204049f07?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjm=
lXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decorati=
on: underline;">unbeatable </a><strong><a href=3D"https://link.sbstck.com/r=
edirect/796c268b-a9f1-4f85-ae43-6c5204049f07?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7=
GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); =
text-decoration: underline;">scale economies</a></strong><span>, until a de=
cade into the company&#8217;s life. The uncertainty and difficulty of its r=
ocket capabilities gave it a big enough headstart that it didn&#8217;t need=
 to worry about long-term moats too early.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"colo=
r: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;=
">Often, though, it&#8217;s useful to identify two challenges to start atta=
cking immediately:</p><ol style=3D"margin-top: 0; padding: 0;"><li style=3D=
"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, =
64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; p=
adding-left: 4px;">The thing you need to prove to reduce uncertainty (novel=
 or complexity).&#160;</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=
=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-h=
eight: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">The path to d=
efensibility.&#160;</p></li></ol><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-s=
ize: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">With that, you&#8217;ve =
completed the diagnosis. You understand the competitive landscape, the why =
now, roughly how long of an uncertainty window you&#8217;ll have, which moa=
ts you need to have in place when it runs out, and the couple of core chall=
enges you&#8217;ll need to address.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64,=
 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">It might see=
m like a lot, but at the end of the diagnosis, you&#8217;ve sanity-checked =
your idea and simplified a ton of complexity into just a couple of obstacle=
s to overcome. Now it&#8217;s time to translate that work into decisions ab=
out how your company will operate.&#160;</p><h3 class=3D"header-with-anchor=
