nA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); t=
ext-decoration: underline;">wrote about in June</a><span>, is a beautiful e=
xample of a diagnosis informing a guiding policy with an eye towards defens=
ibility.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16p=
x; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><a href=3D"https://link.sbstck.c=
