after realizing declining launch costs could make space manufacturing econo=
mics work.</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; l=
ine-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">His diagnosis: Varda needed to excel=
 at manufacturing, returning payloads, and selling. Focusing on both commer=
cial and government customers could help it gain advantages and develop sca=
