ng: border-box; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;=
 margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">Brought on experts in tho=
se 3 areas: Will Bruey for reentry, Adrian Radocea for manufacturing, Eric =
Lasker for sales.</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special-fo=
rmat: bullet;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); =
font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-le=
ft: 4px;">Prioritized speed with experienced hires &#8212; &#8220;the train=
